info.name: Uber Eats Menu API
info.description:
This collection demonstrates all of the endpoints supported by the **Uber Eats Menu API**.

The following environment variables are required to generate access tokens, and can be found in the Developer Dashboard (use the **Uber Eats APIs** environment template):

- `uber_api_client_id`
- `uber_api_client_secret`

request.description: Ensure your environment has a `client_id` and `client_secret` environment variable.
Ensure your environment has a `client_id` and `client_secret` environment variable.
